title: Remove EndorsementType from GraphQL types __init__.py
description: Edit `src/backend/app/graphql/types/__init__.py` to remove the import and re-export of `EndorsementType`. Ensure the GraphQL schema can still be assembled without this type.
acceptance_criteria:
- No `EndorsementType` import in types/__init__.py
- No `EndorsementType` in `__all__` list (if present)
- GraphQL schema assembles successfully
- Backend starts without errors
